the biggest changes that we made was instituting

00:49.020 --> 01:01.071
the Student Management Information System, 
SIMS, I think we call it. in which the whole record,

01:01.675 --> 01:11.293
the admissions and records keeping thing was, I 
would say, computerized, to use a better word on

01:01.675 --> 01:11.293
the thing. But it's a process in which the 
application, from application to graduation is

01:11.894 --> 01:23.717
now kept in a uniform records system which you can 
follow the student from the very beginning until

01:24.288 --> 01:29.373
the time that they graduate. It was quite 
