13:05.368 --> 13:10.554
for a lot of students. Would you restrict it as to 
major? Would you link it to any particular major?

13:15.239 --> 13:18.323
No, I wouldn't link it to major because I've seen 
too many students change too many majors. Uh,

13:18.742 --> 13:27.752
they, you know, students coming in, they just 
don't have enough experience to know what they

13:18.742 --> 13:27.752
want to be their major. And, you know, on a related 
subject, they are, for that reason, I think

13:28.432 --> 13:43.068
there's some merit in university colleges and 
some other things of that nature, which you, it can

13:28.432 --> 13:43.068
keep students, I think, from feeling, quote, that 
they're a failure because they got in the wrong

13:28.432 --> 13:43.068
field. Uh, having been in the wrong field myself at 
one time, I can have some sympathy for that. All

